Depending on the design elements, light and dark color schemes are automatically set be the system using the colors you provide here.

fields.instructions: Use this option to show or hide developer related items from the Wordpress admin menu.

fields.label: E-Commerce
fields.name: show_ecommerce
fields.instructions: Use this option to enable e-commerce plugins and content rows. Online store requires Woo commerce plugin, plugin configuration, stripe account, and active SSL on hosting server.

fields.label: Events
fields.name: show_events
fields.instructions: Use this option to enable Events Calendar content row and post type.

fields.label: Projects Portfolio
fields.name: show_projects_portfolio
fields.instructions: Use this option to add a portfolio of projects to the site. This option enables a new custom post type, as well as additional flexible content rows in the admin.

fields.label: Testimonials
fields.name: show_testimonials
fields.instructions: Use this option to add customer / client testimonials to the site. This option enables a new custom post type, as well as additional flexible content rows in the admin.
